@PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress = http://localhost:5221

### =============================================================================
### LOAD TEST ENDPOINT - For Azure Load Testing
### =============================================================================

### Load Test - Default parameters (tuned for Premium0V3)
GET {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/loadtest
Accept: application/json

###

### Load Test - Custom CPU work (high CPU stress)
GET {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/loadtest?workIterations=10000&bufferSizeKb=2000&baselineDelayMs=0&softLimit=500&degradationFactor=25
Accept: application/json

###

### Load Test - Memory pressure scenario
GET {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/loadtest?workIterations=20&bufferSizeKb=100000&baselineDelayMs=100&softLimit=100&degradationFactor=125
Accept: application/json

###

### Load Test - Thread pool only (no CPU work)
GET {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/loadtest?workIterations=0&bufferSizeKb=2000&baselineDelayMs=500&softLimit=25&degradationFactor=500
Accept: application/json

###

### Load Test - High concurrency scenario
GET {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/loadtest?workIterations=100&bufferSizeKb=10000&baselineDelayMs=200&softLimit=250&degradationFactor=50
Accept: application/json

###

### Load Test Statistics
GET {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/loadtest/stats
Accept: application/json

