### =============================================================================
### SIMULATION CONTROLS
### =============================================================================

### Trigger High CPU (10 seconds)
POST {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/cpu/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "durationSeconds": 10
}

###

### Allocate Memory (512 MB)
POST {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/memory/allocate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sizeMegabytes": 512
}

###

### Release Memory
POST {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/memory/release
Accept: application/json

###

### Block Threads
POST {{PerfProblemSimulator_HostAddress}}/api/threadblock/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "delaySeconds": 10,
    "concurrentCount": 100
}

